                    <span>This book is useless for any work or learning.<br> <br>All samples are made with authors' functions which are in compiled dll written in C++ !?<p>Each chapter has at least 30% about porting from Win16 to Win32.<p>And book is filled with listings of forms and projects.<p>If you remove all this from book, the rest is less than 100 pages with confused explanations.<p>Do not buy this book. There are much better books around.</span>
                  
